      "file": "src/components/PageViewer.tsx",
      "root_cause": "ResizeObserver effect ([] deps) ran once at mount while active was null, so the container ref was null and the effect returned early without observing. When a page was selected the effect never re-ran, cssWidth stayed 0, and the render effect bailed on `cssWidth === 0`. Canvas stayed blank.",
